习惯。提醒 10 月 13 日以来有葛仙山镇旅居史，在上述时间段与核酸检测阳性人员有接触或轨迹有交叉的人员，立即向社区和工作单位报告，配合做好核酸检测、健康监测等管控措施。江西铅山 +1，全县红绿灯调整至红灯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e97c0831844c7303b50a15957d4a424a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "192 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495606443"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDcyNDE1NjEwIJ6r9YsGMAQ4bkAIcgk0OTU2MDY0NDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1635667704.3140757", "card_id": "Q_492563038", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "咖啡喝多了对健康有害吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a7e9a52b756849edc8745da6b566e0d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "185 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/492563038"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDcxNzQwMDA1IJ2/pIsGMAA4wgFACXIJNDkyNTYzMDM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1635667704.3143709", "card_id": "Q_495271969", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国产动画《斗破苍穹三年之约》（特别篇 3）10 月 31 日开播，你感觉如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-35198283d12e65fc6feb1d52c31c6893_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "178 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495271969"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDcyMzQxNTMwII+B7osGMAE4xQFACnIJNDk1MjcxOTY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1635667704.3147986", "card_id": "Q_58897556", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 316}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "山姆会员店（sam's club）有什么值得