序、破坏城市形象的行为，将依法依规进行处置。 当前国内出现多点散发疫情，全球疫情仍在扩散蔓延，在此，提醒广大来泉游客及旅行社及时关注泉州本地疫情防控规定，按要求做好疫情防控措施，确保旅游行程顺利进行。 （来源：法制日报） 10 月 28 日，福建泉州。一导游对游客称「我只要一个电话，你就在这边待着，14 天回不去」。泉州市文化广电和旅游局工作人员告诉记者，已关注到此事，正在排查。（来源：澎湃新闻）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e25b0ef3ffdaa6f4e5b8a580fbe88317_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495328770"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDcyMzU0MTc0INPh7osGMAs4pQNAFXIJNDk1MzI4NzcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1635667704.3198144", "card_id": "Q_483037837", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 186}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "今年 T1 有可能夺冠吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6d42e2a57da3bbc387c32c43dbbc3139_720w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "43 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/483037837"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDY5NjIzNTg2IKycpokGMAY4/gFAFnIJNDgzMDM3ODM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1635667704.320221", "card_id": "Q_495145560", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 382}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "现在全网都在劝退生化环材，等到这方面的人才供应出现稀缺了，他们的价值会不会大幅上升？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-30c9713880e548079272da4b65792f15_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/495145560"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgdW4nPfahrA+EAMaCDcyMzEzMzY3II+n6osGMDA4vgpAF3IJNDk1MTQ1NTYweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1635667704.3205712", "card_id": "Q_49